Text.string: What the crab-anus are you even saying?
You speak nonsense. Please speak, um... yes-sense.
Sorry, my lovely, could we try that once more?
Okay, the rules are very complicated. Pick the right answer before the other guy, or you get zapped. Got it? Doesn't matter. Let's go.
I choose A! It's gotta be A!
This one's B! I choose B!
I know this one. It's B!
I'm gonna kill you after this. You know that, right?
Uh oh, they're on to me/you. You know what to do.
You won! Yay you! Uh, FYI, most bandit game shows end in a bloodbath.
Yeahhh! GET SOME! Let's do some friggin' trivia!
Except for the game, Bloodbath, which traditionally ends in a saucy dance off!
Win it for the Twin Gods!
YEAH! Show that Vault Thief you know stuff!
Okay, I'm hacking into the show's systems now. She is telling you to ready up! Oh, she's so amazing. Hit the button!
(uproarious laughter; imitates “wrong noise” buzzer, continues laughing)
Oh my rippling PECS! That is Zahnzi Kall! She hosts the hottest bandit game show on Pandora! Oh, you gotta win that contest so she and I can be in love forever. Do it. Do it. Do it. Do it.
Okay, okay, gotta... gotta hand it to 'em. Fine.
Uh, I... did not see that coming. I... well, sure.
It's okay, it's okay, we'll... we'll get 'em next time. It's... it's gonna be all right.
Ehhh... they get it right, they get it right. I guess.
Wha—||Okay, um... uh, no—no worries. It's fine! We'll get it back.
They weren't supposed to do that!
That BETTER be the last one they get.
I've got money riding on this, asshole!
What the hell do you think you're tryin' to pull?
That sonuvabitch just got one right! What the crap?!
Oh, I KNOW they didn't just get the right answer!
How DARE they get an answer right on OUR turf?!
I hate right answers! I REALLY hate right answers!
Eh, I... guess that's fine. Did they cheat?
Are you kidd— ugh. All right, fine, give it to 'em, yay.
Ohh... ugh, ick. I guess they're good. Hnh.
Ugh, all right. All's fair in love and whatever.
Really? Is that really right? Hnh, okay.
Blaagk! Brlrhgrjrk, glrlkrkrl! Blkhrkrk, blrkr? Blkrh.
“Which bandit throws the best murder parties—Vaughn the Ripped, or Magdumb Opie?”||—I think we, heh, probably know the answer to this one.
I said pick me! Come on, bro! What are you tryna do here?!
All right, they're gonna get suspicious if I change all the questions, so... this one actually says, “Who is the most handsome Pandoran overlord of all time?” Is it: Handsome Jack, or Troy Calypso?
Just give 'em what they want. Pick Troy.
A total narcissist, sure, but, uh... yeah... um... actually has no redeeming qualities whatsoever.
Okay, she likes shirtless guys with shredded torsos. Okay! This party's picking up!

Man, is she scary or what? I love her so much. I'm so in love! Oh, I wanna have her babies. I have a plan to impress her. I'm gonna hack into the game show and I'm just gonna change some things around Vaughn-style, and don't you worry! I will translate for you, because I speak bandit, and you do not.

Next up: who—oh, heh, I know the answer to this one. “Who has the sexiest, most sculpted-est abs in the galaxy?” Come on, you know this one. Huh, is it me? Ungh! Is it this guy? Ungh! Is he doin' it now? Ungh, yeah! Get it, get it, get it, son!
Bluhgh, ragh-raaaghl rgrh, blrbrbrb, bluhgh, r-rghrghgrgrgrh blrgrhgh!
“Who's the most powerful Siren and also our... savior... and the image of perfection in every way.” Hoo, boy...
Ugh, okay. You know what they wanna hear.
Ugh, that Tyreen Calypso... Aghhhh! BLOOD FEUD!
All right, it is time to seal this deal. I can't lose!
Byagrhr, brlrghrh brlrgrh, lagghrlgah. Byaghagh? Rgrbhrgrhr.
“What eligible bandit bachelor sporting a sweet cape and abs of steel should Zahnzi totally go on a date with?” What? Oh, wow. That is a good question.
Who is this freakin' guy? Does anyone know this dork?!
She can't take her eyes off of me! Ha-HA! Side note: I totally rigged the game so you'd win no matter how hard you tried to suck. Congrats!
FILTHY CHEATERS! I can't stand cheaters!

Ooh! She's asking about me! Okay-okay-okay, okay... Tell her what a super swell guy I am, and also that I'm the most—oh, write this down—bloodthirsty death-king on the planet, and... I am strong, and... have a powerful butt.
Vaughn is the most bloodthirsty death-king on the planet. And also swell, or whatever.
Fella's pretty cut, you know? I saw him crush a rival bandit chief's head between his pecs. Just sayin'.
Vaughn is an impressive specimen. His bloodlust is rivaled only by his mating prowess. Rawr!
Me and you, it'll never happen. But Vaughn—ohhhhh, he's a top... tier fella. Good lad, that one. Have a go.

Ah, man! She's calling me! I gotta go. You're the best friend a death-king could ever ask for!||—Hey, Zahnz! What's up, girl? Just, you know, sitting on my bone throne. That's a throne made of bones. What are you up to? Uh huh. Uh huh. Uh huh. Do you wanna see my butt?
YEAH! I can't wait to watch y'all get zapped!
Wooohoo! Hell yeah! I love you, Zahnzi!
Blkrh! Bragh, blrhrrk. Blrhrrjrghkh. Blrjrhk, brjkrhgrk.
